name: (on Foundation) Whispering memories to the moon

metadata.name: Concussion
metadata.description:
January 24, 2022, a rainy day 07:10 in the morning. 

I was driving on the highway and suddenly saw two big lights in my rearview mirror. At the same time my car started spinning, it seemed like an hour before it stopped. When I got out I was confused. I wanted to cross on the highway to flee, but someone stopped me. 

Who are all those people? 
what happened? 
where is my girlfriend? 

There was a truck that hit me, the confusion continues. A concussion said the doctor where I suddenly sat.

How did I get here?
Where am I going?
where did my car go?

It only takes a second to change or wipe out everything you have and are. But it takes ages to realize what happened, and why. At least if you still get that time.

Actually, this concussion is causing something else. A wake-up call. Life is too short to do things you don't want to do. So I'll stop with that right now. My future is in art. My path changes there. Promised. 

This is the meaning behind this NFT concussion I made visual 1/1.
